Definition: a grammatical category used in the classification of pronouns, possessive determiners, and verb forms according to whether they indicate the speaker, the addressee, or a third party
Example: stop talking about yourself in the third person
Synonyms: grammatical_category, a, grammatical, category, used, in, the, classification, of, pronouns, possessive, determiners, and, verb, forms, according, to, whether, they, indicate, speaker, addressee, or, third, party, stop, talking, about, yourself
Category: noun.communication
